{{Infobox journal | title = Latin American Journal of Sedimentology and Basin Analysis | formernames = Revista de la Asociación Argentina de Sedimentología | cover = | discipline = [[Sedimentology]], [[Earth sciences]] | abbreviation = Lat. Am. J. Sedimentol. Basin Anal. | language = English, Spanish | editor = | publisher = [[Asociación Argentina de Sedimentología]] | country = Argentina | history = 1994–present | frequency = Biannually | website = http://www.sedimentologia.org.ar/ | link1 = | link1-name = Online access | link2 = http://sedimentologia.org.ar/spa/revista/ediciones-anteriores/ | link2-name = Online archive | link3 = http://www.scielo.org.ar/scielo.php?script=sci_serial&pid=1851-4979 | link3-name = Journal page at [[SciELO]] | ISSN = 1851-4979 | eISSN = 1669-7316 | OCLC = | LCCN = }} '''''Latin American Journal of Sedimentology and Basin Analysis''''' (formerly '''''Revista de la Asociación Argentina de Sedimentología''''') is a biannual [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[scientific journal]] published by the [[Asociación Argentina de Sedimentología]]. The journal covers the field of [[sedimentology]] and [[sedimentary basin]] analysis.
